{"categories":["non-profit","events","seasonal-promotion","global-observances-celebrations"],"collections":"","description":"This email template is perfect for non-profits planning events or seasonal promotions around International Women's Day on March 8. It's vibrant with shades of purple, signifying dignity and self-respect, which are synonymous with the spirit of the day. The template is designed to effectively communicate the essence of the celebration, while also encouraging participation in fundraising initiatives. Ideal for global observances and celebrations, it allows organizations to honor women's contributions worldwide. With its visually appealing design and compelling content layout, this template is a great tactic to inspire action and celebrate womanhood on this significant day.","short_description":"Celebrate International Women's Day with our impactful email template. Ideal for non-profits, this template blends purple symbolism with the spirit of fundraising. Perfect for global observances, seasonal promotions, and events, it helps convey your message with style.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/galina-grahovska.jpg","description":"I have gained experience and skills in communications and organization of the work while I was hired in E.Miroglio EAD. I’ve also got excellent French as I was living in France for a few years.\r\n\r\nAbout an year ago, I’ve started designing interfaces and that’s definitely what I was looking for my whole life. I’m using Adobe Photoshop to design websites, emails and mobile apps. I also create prototypes in InVision to make the whole process from the start to the finish much easier.","short_description":"","display_name":"Galina Grahovska","id":"galina-grahovska"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\"><head><title></title><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; cha